value: 7011 - Hotels and Motels Summary > FH-BT NMCS OPERATIONS PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover hotels and motels. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. FH-BT NMCS OPERATIONS PTY LTD is headquartered in Melbourne, Victoria. It is headed by director Chee Teik Gan. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $32.76 million. Its net loss totalled $333,000. FH-BT NMCS OPERATIONS PTY LTD forms part of the services industry sector.
